00:07:44,601 --> 00:07:46,900
Interfaces need to be planned.

125
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:50,983
New vehicles need to be bought.

126
00:07:50,983 --> 00:07:54,459
Again, these different things
need to be coordinated

127
00:07:54,459 --> 00:07:56,982
among each other in order to make

128
00:07:56,982 --> 00:08:01,646
